  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open Hunting XL is a hunting simulator with an emphasis on player freedom. Quickly spot animals using your drone or sneak and spot with binoculars depending on the difficulty you select. Hunt in several locations from Arizona to West Virginia and level up to unlock mechanics seen in no other hunting game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adjustable Difficulty</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/af92f261dd89b5d529069b58d52cc678.poster.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/af92f261dd89b5d529069b58d52cc678.webm?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/af92f261dd89b5d529069b58d52cc678.mp4?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring several difficulty modes from casual to very realistic to make sure everyone gets a good hunt in Open Hunting XL. Use a drone to spot animals easily from the sky or hunt slowly and carefully. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100% Original Shooting Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/8e3f15b8e13195cd793651953e5c9cf6.poster.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/8e3f15b8e13195cd793651953e5c9cf6.webm?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/8e3f15b8e13195cd793651953e5c9cf6.mp4?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open Hunting XL has very unique shooting mechanics. You will have to pull the trigger, watch your breath and much more to get a good shot off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Realistic animal behavior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An emphasis on small game hunting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Rewarding, patient hunting at high difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing, quick hunting, at lower difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several locations to hunt in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique shooting mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/452d736b55cd152205658ec2dea23f77.poster.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/452d736b55cd152205658ec2dea23f77.webm?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/452d736b55cd152205658ec2dea23f77.mp4?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/acc54bef9b757e315d8af9a063e10ae8.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open Hunting XL is a hunting simulator with an emphasis on player freedom. Quickly spot animals using your drone or sneak and spot with binoculars depending on the difficulty you select. Hunt in several locations from Arizona to West Virginia and level up to unlock mechanics seen in no other hunting game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adjustable Difficulty</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/af92f261dd89b5d529069b58d52cc678.poster.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/af92f261dd89b5d529069b58d52cc678.webm?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/af92f261dd89b5d529069b58d52cc678.mp4?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring several difficulty modes from casual to very realistic to make sure everyone gets a good hunt in Open Hunting XL. Use a drone to spot animals easily from the sky or hunt slowly and carefully. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100% Original Shooting Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/8e3f15b8e13195cd793651953e5c9cf6.poster.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/8e3f15b8e13195cd793651953e5c9cf6.webm?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/8e3f15b8e13195cd793651953e5c9cf6.mp4?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open Hunting XL has very unique shooting mechanics. You will have to pull the trigger, watch your breath and much more to get a good shot off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Realistic animal behavior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An emphasis on small game hunting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Rewarding, patient hunting at high difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing, quick hunting, at lower difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several locations to hunt in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique shooting mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/452d736b55cd152205658ec2dea23f77.poster.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/452d736b55cd152205658ec2dea23f77.webm?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/452d736b55cd152205658ec2dea23f77.mp4?t=1732100626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545380/extras/acc54bef9b757e315d8af9a063e10ae8.avif?t=1732100626\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p>",
